{"tid":2117484,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"入呢個 Uber driver 邀請碼賺350蚊！","createTime":"2020-07-21T01:28:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T03:11:38.000Z","uid":212080,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f3df946e9f5ef03f1d0383359d33839ea4753485","tid":2117484,"uid":212080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T01:28:30.000Z","msg":"各位ching呢排日日留喺屋企會唔會好悶？不如一齊做Uber driver送送外賣揾啲錢幫補家計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n步兵每單收入大概係25蚊，小弟試過好多次用5分鐘由屋企樓下送去隔籬100公尺內嘅大廈就輕鬆賺到25蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家註冊時入呢個邀請碼：<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">dbt04l </span></strong>做夠30單仲可以多賺350蚊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲諗乜嘢啊，快啲一齊做步兵揾快錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c2535c5054ea51a476a7ece459221a9fbaa66b","tid":2117484,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T01:29:45.000Z","msg":"搵生意搵到上連登"},{"pid":"51629cc4f11411ad012a3c8ad5689cdd5833f0a4","tid":2117484,"uid":5995,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T01:31:52.000Z","msg":"Uber eat出名遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />狗也不屌"},{"pid":"0f8770f637f37e03f30c3713c41af40ee2a6041e","tid":2117484,"uid":333283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T03:11:38.000Z","msg":"你咪好賺 無本生利<br />\n睬你都傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}